                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Design tools are software applications and platforms that assist designers in creating and
                            visualizing their design concepts. These tools provide a range of functionalities and
                            features that support various aspects of the design process.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
